data.description: This home is in a newer neighborhood in Copperas Cove with access to a community pool for the HOA. Want a pool without the maintenance? This house is for you! The HOA also offers a community park. This home offers a split floor plan with 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms with lots of natural light. The Living room is open to the kitchen showing off the beautiful granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and under mount sink located in the island. The owner's suite offers a full sized shower, double vanity, linen closet, and walk in closet. The laundry room is conveniently located near the garage. Schedule a showing on your future home!
